reviewText: Hardcore art! Image quality is much better than the dodgy VHS copies that used to float around. This is probably as good as this one's going to get.
It had Edy Williams in it.......thats all.
I can FINALLY retire my old VHS copy of Dr. Minx! Not the greatest of it's kind but the only Edy Williams starring vehicle from that era.  Sound and picture pretty excellent when compared to VHS.
This is a true collectible and will be archived. Thank you.
